{"tid":2198291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"光榮冰室老闆入一入黎","createTime":"2020-09-11T08:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T03:32:07.000Z","uid":92836,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bd56e4e40cc23e7ef7c15a2754d2d3c20ee8bef3","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T08:58:30.000Z","msg":"首先我真係好鐘意食呢間黃店，由寂寂無名嘅冰室$45連凍飲嘅XO叉燒炒蛋飯一路食到依加<br />\n又平又抵食我lunch time日日食咁濟<br />\n但你哋個廚房衛生可唔可以搞好啲？<br />\n成日見到入面啲人口罩又唔戴係到整野食<br />\n仲有你杯檸茶加咩動物嘅腳俾我？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">政治表態有良心、<br />\n整野食都俾翻啲良心我</span>，<br />\n老細可唔可以落去分店多啲巡下場？唔該！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cPZnzYt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcPZnzYt.png&h=127b5300&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOerhbT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOerhbT.png&h=82eec241&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cREF55n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcREF55n.png&h=0869f92a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\">請立即停止光顧 光榮冰室 呢間垃圾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121949</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n之前睇過呢篇文都只係認為其中一小部份嘅個別例子，依加真仲要停埋個三萬完蛋飯，真係食唔落，仲有幾時搞翻好個衛生？一直keep住係咁，黃店都無面俾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚鍾意食光榮"},{"pid":"9d8e6220e46f7639ff3ea645b223c05f3ca7e55f","tid":2198291,"uid":354439,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"旺角嗰間特別污糟,<br />\n 廚房佬唔著衫唔戴口罩<br />\n好多螞蟻喺張枱度行<br />\n以上係我親身體驗"},{"pid":"7083e349ce92984236c303c210962c4371fac168","tid":2198291,"uid":249960,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bf963026148023b84f503aa304103145bee528","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T10:15:39.000Z","msg":"推俾老細睇"},{"pid":"ff5fce4a1dce5f8107779fef8d60630cef445ae1","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:06:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e5fc01957fde699abca8fb5c3ee758824a7a28a","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你地"},{"pid":"04b477fab7e3f581c38ae2c4ee5fb85bb4040a1b","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"223f3c65739bc08c51b76886ab0d0c2f5b289d08","tid":2198291,"uid":138197,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"未飲叫佢換囉 唔講黃藍 好多茶記都係污糟嫁啦 中過伏就冇下次嫁啦"},{"pid":"eb08ab70ab578cb350ee65bee55d1b1fdde81ad1","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223f3c65739bc08c51b76886ab0d0c2f5b289d08","tid":2198291,"uid":138197,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"未飲叫佢換囉 唔講黃藍 好多茶記都係污糟嫁啦 中過伏就冇下次嫁啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"你都癲"},{"pid":"2e052a4f00bd2277bff4b67c36848a44ba4a0df9","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:33:35.000Z","msg":"點解唔接受批評，諗唔明"},{"pid":"8f39a1513394fe33ed0dcefc3b2b1b58ccfc14e8","tid":2198291,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb08ab70ab578cb350ee65bee55d1b1fdde81ad1","tid":2198291,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223f3c65739bc08c51b76886ab0d0c2f5b289d08","tid":2198291,"uid":138197,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T05:32:13.000Z","msg":"未飲叫佢換囉 唔講黃藍 好多茶記都係污糟嫁啦 中過伏就冇下次嫁啦"},"